43
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:36,240
Selling some ore.

44
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,440
Jiaojiao is leaving.

45
00:03:37,640 --> 00:03:38,480
I wanted to make more money

46
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:40,340
